### UPDATE
### Modificar un producto
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "CHALECO SALVAVIDAS ACTUALIZADO",
    "price": 59.99,
    "quantity": 8
}

### UPDATE 2 - Cambiar tipo (quitar articleType y agregar kayakType)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleType": null,
    "kayakType": 3
}

### UPDATE 3 - Intentar quitar ambos tipos (debe fallar)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleType": null,
    "kayakType": null
}

### DELETE
### Borrar un producto
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToDelete}}

### IDs
@idToGet = {{createProductToGet.response.body.data.id}}
@idToUpdate = {{createProductToUpdate.response.body.data.id}}
@idToDelete = {{createProductToDelete.response.body.data.id}}